{"tid":1497193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【823 香港之路】要記得，今日係紀念波羅的海之路三十週年","createTime":"2019-08-23T00:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:34:00.000Z","uid":70493,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a504dc3977eda63aab6d582800e715caa23a6789","tid":1497193,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"今日係紀念波羅的海之路 (The Baltic Way) 三十週年<br />\n唔知有冇人會帶波羅的海三國國旗？<br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞 Estonia<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irD8ewS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirD8ewS.png&h=0969b6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉脫維亞 Latvia<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BpWoqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BpWoqc.png&h=2fb45b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立陶宛 Lithuania<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPr2iYx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPr2iYx.png&h=caa1b498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果有外國記者問起，希望大家要記得三個國家嘅名，<br />\n佢地係抵抗蘇聯的佔領而全民和平抗爭組成人鏈，<br />\n而最終佢地都得到獨立。<br />\n<br />\n見好似冇乜人講今晚活動，請幫忙置頂！"},{"pid":"f11114b11912690a2eb49279af637e5c58e249fa","tid":1497193,"uid":70493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/hkway\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkway&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=f8090b2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/hkway</a><br />\n《香港之路 The Hong Kong Way》<br />\n日期：2019年8月23日（星期五）<br />\n時間：7-9pm<br />\n1900 在指定集合點外集合<br />\n2000 自發手牽手形成香港之路<br />\n2100 流水式散去<br />\n集合地點：#港島線 #荃灣線 #觀塘線 指定港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請集中三線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n‼注意事項‼<br />\n1) 無特定Dresscode<br />\n2) 聽到熟悉既歌曲 (如Do you hear the people sing) 邀請各位大大聲一齊唱<br />\n3) 有航拍機飛過嘅時候請開起電flashlight<br />\n(怕唔方便舉電話既可以自備螢光棒 頭燈等發光物品)<br />\n4) 馬路 唔方便企人位 可以以雷射筆連起 但唔係個個有 義工都另外準備左d絲帶<br />\n5) 各位注意安全 參加者和平理性非暴力 不作出任何違法行為 遇上重大危險人鏈會解散及離開<br />\n<br />\nLinks<br />\n823 香港之路頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKWay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKWay&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ba1cac73\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKWay</a><br />\n<br />\n823 香港之路公海群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=abcda59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw</a><br />\n<br />\n路線地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/viewer?mid=1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ&amp;ll=22.32288133674603%2C114.18210443909493&amp;z=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F1%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ%26ll%3D22.32288133674603%252C114.18210443909493%26z%3D13&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=a6a6fc77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/viewer?mid=1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ&amp;ll=22.32288133674603%2C114.18210443909493&amp;z=13</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/香港之路-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=32c67d3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/香港之路-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkway823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkway823&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=39c98dfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkway823</a>"},{"pid":"35f317de2099c205213708f432e5e802f7157652","tid":1497193,"uid":70493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/McVZfva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcVZfva.jpg&h=be863aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ &amp; A<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQ1. 我去邊都得, 點知邊度缺人?<br />\nA1. TG channel會用嚟作即時發佈~ <a href=\"https://t.me/HKWay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKWay&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ba1cac73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKWay</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2. 馬路點連?<br />\nA2. 不阻塞交通 綠燈連 又或者用創意既手法連~ 又或者唔連~ Be Water!<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 開手機燈點拖手?<br />\nA3. 大家一齊右手拎手機 左手拖住隔離既人既右手~<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 幾時要開燈?<br />\nA4. 覺得差唔多形成人鏈就開得啦~<br />\n<br />\nQ5. 會唔會有路線圖?<br />\nA5. 我地一有確實既路線圖就會公佈google map link俾大家~<br />\n<br />\nQ6. 有無dress code?<br />\nA6. 無dress code~ 擔心會落雨既人士可以帶傘~<br />\n<br />\nQ7. 除左文宣果三條線外 其他路線係咪你地有份搞?<br />\nA7. 係其他網民自發搞既<br />\n<br />\nQ8. 係咪一定要7點到?<br />\nA8. 組成人鏈需時都需要熱心既你地幫手! 多你一個多好多~ 希望大家可以7點到! 唔能夠7點到既都歡迎到時加入架!!!<br />\n<br />\nQ9. 我果區無集合點/路線 我可以去邊?<br />\nA9. 麻煩留意Tg channel 邊度唔夠人就去邊度~ 或者3條線隨便去一個位~<br />\n<br />\nQ10. 係咪會有人影相?<br />\nA10. 呢個活動既目的之一係想俾全世界都望到香港發生咩事~ 關注香港~ 我地歡迎媒體，熱心市民同埋好奇街坊影相~"},{"pid":"7fab25fdbbccfd42069154899cdf1d09c4bf4ce8","tid":1497193,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:53:55.000Z","msg":"[8.23香港之路]邊個站最多學生妹 應該去邊個站好?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496995</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"355b6593a7577f4b123965ad6ef23b476bd3d6ea","tid":1497193,"uid":70493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/u1ZOTim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%